<script>
    jq(document).ready(function () {
        var navItems = jq("#navGlobal ul li[data-section-segment]");
        var activeFound = false;
        var index;
        for (index = 0; index < navItems.length; index++) {
            var item = jq(navItems[index]);
            item.removeClass('active');
            if (!activeFound && window.location.href.toLowerCase().indexOf(navItems[index].attributes["data-section-segment"].value) > -1) {
                item.addClass('active');
                activeFound = true;
            }
        }
        jq('#navMain ul li a[href*="News-Events-and-Training"]').removeClass("activeMain");
        if (window.location.href.indexOf("News-and-Events") != -1) {
            jq('#navMain ul li a[href*="News-Events-and-Training"]').addClass("activeMain");
        }
    });
</script>

<script>
    var twitterAttemptCount = 0;

    jq(document).ready(function () {
        jq('.mainBlockContainer .imgText').hover(function () {
            jq('.extra', this).fadeToggle();
            jq('.img', this).fadeToggle();
            jq('.h3Div', this).toggleClass('h3DivH');
        });

        jq('.homepageCarouselContainer').show();
        jq('.homepageCarousel').appendTo('.homepageCarouselContainer');
        jq('.alert').appendTo('.homepageSysAlertContainer .container');
        jq('.homepageSysAlertContainer').show();

        jq('.homepageCarousel').addClass('nmt');
        jq('.btn-primary').parent().css('margin', '0');

        setTimeout(showLatestNews, 100);
    });

    function showLatestNews() {
        if (isTwitterFeedDisplayed()) {
            return;
        }
        twitterAttemptCount++;
        if (twitterAttemptCount < 50) {
            setTimeout(showLatestNews, 100);
            return;
        }
        jq('.news').show();
        jq('.homepageMsrbTweet, .msrbTweet').hide();
    }

    function isTwitterFeedDisplayed() {
        return jq('a.twitter-timeline').length == 0;
    }
</script>
